Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.87,0:01:35.86,Main Dialogue Top,R,0,0,0,,Toin oin!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.86,0:01:37.74,Main Dialogue,Pochi,0,0,0,,Essa é a única conclusão.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.74,0:01:40.05,Main Dialogue,Yuzuka,0,0,0,,Sei...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.05,0:01:41.33,Main Dialogue,Chiya,0,0,0,,Isso é preconceito.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.05,0:01:59.78,Internal Dialogue,Yuzuka,0,0,0,,Um grupo de estudos?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.78,0:02:01.12,Internal Dialogue,Yuzuka,0,0,0,,Seria de grande ajuda.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.12,0:02:04.22,Internal Dialogue,Chiya,0,0,0,,Realmente tem muitas coisas que eu não entendo...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.69,0:02:07.72,Main Dialogue,Pochi,0,0,0,,Eu pensei que elas iriam dizer isso...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.23,0:02:10.95,Main Dialogue,Pochi,0,0,0,,Como falo isso pra Mafuyu?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.66,0:02:12.98,Main Dialogue,Pochi,0,0,0,,É que sabe...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.47,0:02:15.48,Flashback Dialogue,Mafuyu,0,0,0,,Elas são minhas kouhais.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.48,0:02:18.67,Flashback Dialogue,Mafuyu,0,0,70,,Fico pensando se eu poderia ajudá-las de alguma forma como senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.67,0:02:22.03,Flashback Dialogue,Pochi,0,0,70,,Se quiser fazer algo que todos os estudantes fazem, tente um grupo de estudos.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.03,0:02:23.66,Flashback Dialogue,Mafuyu,0,0,70,,Um grupo de estudos...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.66,0:02:25.03,Flashback Dialogue,Mafuyu,0,0,70,,Parece ótimo!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.04,0:02:29.25,Main Dialogue,Pochi,0,0,70,,Eu não esperava que elas fossem garotas mágicas que vão bem na escola.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.71,0:02:31.41,Main Dialogue,Miton,0,0,70,,Eu te entendo.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.41,0:02:33.17,Main Dialogue,Miton,0,0,70,,Vou te dar uma mão.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.05,0:02:35.46,Main Dialogue,Pochi,0,0,70,,Te devo uma.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.46,0:02:37.04,Main Dialogue,Miton,0,0,0,,Isso não é nada.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.47,0:02:38.84,Main Dialogue,Miton,0,0,0,,Somos colegas, não somos?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.12,0:02:43.12,Main Dialogue,Miton,0,0,0,,Pronto, pronto.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.12,0:02:44.63,Main Dialogue,Pochi,0,0,0,,Miton!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.50,0:02:50.35,Main Dialogue,Chiya,0,0,0,,Sabe, você poderia simplesmente ter nos chamado para tomar chá. {asked to tea.}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.30,0:02:53.97,Main Dialogue,Miton,0,0,0,,Tem razão. Isso é verdade!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.97,0:02:56.29,Main Dialogue,Miton,0,0,0,,Que bom que perguntei pra você, Chiya!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.66,0:02:59.77,Main Dialogue,Chiya,0,0,0,,Você achou que éramos amigos agora?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.27,0:03:03.11,Main Dialogue,Chiya,0,0,0,,Acontece que eu só fico de boa \Nquando a Yuzuka está por perto.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.11,0:03:06.16,Main Dialogue,Chiya,0,0,0,,Quando a Yuzuka não está, eu quero que você me chame pelo sobrenome.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.16,0:03:08.95,Main Dialogue,Miton,0,0,0,,Vou fazer isso a partir de agora, Sakagami-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.22,0:03:11.81,Main Dialogue,Yuzuka,0,0,0,,Tomar chá?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.81,0:03:14.96,Main Dialogue,Chiya,0,0,70,,É, a Mafuyu-san nos convidou.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.96,0:03:16.53,Main Dialogue,Yuzuka,0,0,70,,No sábado, né?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.53,0:03:17.80,Main Dialogue,Yuzuka,0,0,70,,Por mim tudo bem.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.80,0:03:19.98,Main Dialogue,Chiya,0,0,70,,Então vou falar pra ela.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.98,0:03:21.63,Internal Dialogue,Miton,0,0,70,,Isso foi fácil.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.63,0:03:25.47,Main Dialogue,Chiya,0,0,70,,Neste sábado, gostaria de admirar e apreciar a Yuzuka comigo?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.78,0:03:27.05,Main Dialogue,Yuzuka,0,0,0,,Espera aí...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.22,0:03:29.26,Main Dialogue,Mafuyu,0,0,0,,Uou!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.81,0:03:32.40,Main Dialogue,Mafuyu,0,0,0,,Hmm, o que eu devo dizer?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.40,0:03:35.23,Main Dialogue,Mafuyu,0,0,0,,Imagino o que me faria parecer mais como uma senpai...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.23,0:03:38.70,Main Dialogue,Chiya,0,0,0,,Ela já respondeu.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.70,0:03:39.94,Main Dialogue,Yuzuka,0,0,0,,Deixa eu ver.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.61,0:03:43.53,Internal Dialogue,Mafuyu,0,0,0,,Eu gostaria de admirar e apreciar você também, Chiya-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.28,0:03:49.53,Main Dialogue,Mafuyu,0,0,0,,E então? E então?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.12,0:03:51.03,Main Dialogue,Mafuyu,0,0,0,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.36,0:03:54.54,Internal Dialogue,Chiya,0,0,0,,Então podemos discutir sobre isso outra hora.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.50,0:04:00.30,Main Dialogue,Yuzuka,0,0,0,,Continua.
